      • setGameParameter

        private void setGameParameter​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event,
                              int number_turtle,
                              int interval_turtle,
                              int speed_trutle,
                              int number_log,
                              int interval_log,
                              double speed_log,
                              int number_obstacle,
                              int interval_obstacle,
                              int speed_obstacle)
        This is a MVC design pattern which can load game levels of different difficulties and print the information of parameters
        参数:
        event - the event received from FXML
        number_turtle - the number of turtle
        interval_turtle - the interval between turtles
        speed_trutle - the movement speed of turtle
        number_log - the number of log
        interval_log - the interval between logs
        speed_log - the movement speed of log
        number_obstacle - the number of obstacle
        interval_obstacle - the interval between obstacle
        speed_obstacle - the movement speed of obstacle

      • setPage

        public void setPage​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event,
                    java.lang.String PageName,
                    java.lang.String PageLink)
             throws java.io.IOException
        This is a MVC design pattern which can set the page and print the page information
        参数:
        event - the event received from FXML
        PageName - set the name for the page
        PageLink - set the link for the page
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throw the input/output exceptions
